**Core Tools:**
- `retrieve` - Semantic retrieval from knowledge bases
- `memory` - Agent memory persistence
- `http_request` - API calls and web data fetching
- `file_read` / `file_write` / `editor` - File operations
- `calculator` / `python_repl` - Computation
- `shell` - System command execution
- `use_llm` - Nested agent calls
- `swarm` / `agent_graph` / `workflow` - Multi-agent coordination
